      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，两块数据：找片90，看片10。标签我直接用你刚才说的\"Time spent looking for movie\"和\"Time spent watching it\"，可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
