    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "饼图已经画好了。NETFLIX标题在上方，两块扇区对比很鲜明——找片时间那块占了绝大部分，视觉上冲击力很强。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NETFLIX",
        "Time spent looking for movie",
        "Time spent watching it",
        "pie chart"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "效果符合预期。不过我在想，10%会不会显得太少了？要不要调整到15%，让观看时间的扇区稍微明显一点？",
      "elements_involved": [
